<subSubSection pageId="291" pageNumber="292" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="291" pageNumber="292">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="291" pageNumber="292">The range of this species extends from Long Island, New York to southwestern Wisconsin (Messer 2010: 35), south to the Rio Grande in south-central Texas and southern Florida [see Bousquet 2006c: Fig. 32]; also recorded from the Bahamas (Turnbow and Thomas 2008: 15).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
